name: Erbaly_Nap%27tee
content: Erbaly Nap'tee was an old Nikto woman who lived on Tatooine at the end of the Clone Wars. She was a frequent patron of Dannar's Claim, where her interactions with Annileen Calwell were typified by dementia that prevented her from remembering Annileen or any other employees of the Claim.
